incrementErrorCount

public com.conceptwave.scripting.Integer incrementErrorCount(com.conceptwave.scripting.Boolean enq)
Update Queue error information. Normally called by queue enqueue/dequeue functions.

Parameters:
enq - If true, will update enqueue statistics, if false will update dequeue statistics.
Returns:
For dequeue (enq parameter is false) returns current number of consecutive errors, for enqueue (enq parameter is true) always returns 0

updateStats

public void updateStats(com.conceptwave.scripting.Boolean enq,
                        com.conceptwave.scripting.Integer num,
                        com.conceptwave.scripting.Integer duration)
Update Queue statistical information. Normally called by queue enqueue/dequeue functions.

Parameters:
enq - If true, will update enqueue statistics, if false will update dequeue statistics.
num - Value that used for increasing total number of enqueue or dequeue calls.
duration - Value that used for calculating average time for dequeue processing. Not used for enqueue statistics. Represents number of millisecond that took to process\ dequeue transaction.
